"kind":"italic_en","text":"he weaned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ablactated, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AflAhu","text_ar":"افلاهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AftlAhu","text_ar":"افتلاهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaAhu Eano A^um~ihi","text_ar":"فَلَاهُ عَنْ اُمِّهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AftlAhu","text_ar":"افتلاهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify thus; relating to a colt and a young ass: (S: [and in a similar manner both are expl. in the T, on the authority of ISk:]) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaAhu","text_ar":"فَلَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaAhu Eano A^um~ihi","text_ar":"فَلَاهُ عَنْ اُمِّهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", relating to a colt and a young ass, (T,) signifies thus; (T, M;) but ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AftlAhu","text_ar":"افتلاهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AftlAhu linafosihi","text_ar":"افتلاهُ لِنَفْسِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T,) signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he took him for himself"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from his mother"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (T, M:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falawotuhu","text_ar":"فَلَوْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afolayotuhu","text_ar":"اَفْلَيْتُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I separated him from him mother;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a colt: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuliyat","text_ar":"فُلِيَت"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said of a filly [meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she was separated"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (Msb.) [Hence,] the ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaAp","text_ar":"فَلَاة","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] is [said to be] thus called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liA^an~ahaA fuliyato Eano kul~i xayorK","text_ar":"لِاَنَّهَا فُلِيَتْ عَنْ كُلِّ خَيْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Because it is"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though it were"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weaned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"removed, from everything good"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falawotuhu","text_ar":"فَلَوْتُهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I reared him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brought him up;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[namely, a youth, or boy;] as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aifotalayotuhu","text_ar":"اِفْتَلَيْتُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": a poet says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"walayosa yaholiku min~aA say~idN A^abadFA\n                      \n                     \n                        A_il~aA A@fotalayonaA gulaAmFA say~idFA fiynaA"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And a chief of us does not ever perish but we rear a youth"},{"kind":"text","text":"to be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a chief among us"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaAhu biAls~ayofi","text_ar":"فَلَاهُ بِالسَّيْفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) first pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falawotuhu","text_ar":"فَلَوْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falanotuhu","text_ar":"فَلَنْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falowN","text_ar":"فَلْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faloYN","text_ar":"فَلْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M in this art. and in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"flY","text_ar":"فلى"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He struck"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his head,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the sword:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he struck,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cut, it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. one's head,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the sword."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T * and M in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"flY","text_ar":"فلى"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falawotu","text_ar":"فَلَوْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alqawoma","text_ar":"القَوْمَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I entered amid the breaks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interspaces, of the people;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falayotuhumo","text_ar":"فَلَيْتُهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T, TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaA","text_ar":"فَلَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"as intrans., said of a man,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He journeyed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went forth to journey."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, T, K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became intelligent after being ignorant."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, T, K.)"}],"source_refs":["M","K","S","Msb","TA","T"]},{"entry_id":"n34594","headword_ar":"فَلَاةٌ","root":"flw","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desert such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qafor","text_ar":"قَفْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, K;) so called for a reason mentioned above, in the first paragraph, q. v.; (M;) or ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafaAzap","text_ar":"مَفَازَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T, S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which is no water;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the fewer cases, in which there is an interval of two days with a portion of the day preceding them and of the day following them between the waterings of camels and of one day between the waterings of asses and of sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liloA_ibili riboEN waliloHamiyri","text_ar":"لِلْاـِبِلِ رِبْعٌ وَلِلْحَمِيرِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAlganami gab~N","text_ar":"وَالغَنَمِ غَبٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (M, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a land in which is no water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a wide"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desert such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHoraA='","text_ar":"صَحْرَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falawaAtN","text_ar":"فَلَوَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, M, K,) a pl. of pauc., (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falFA","text_ar":"فَلًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, M, Msb, K,) [or rather this is a coll. gen. n. of which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaApN","text_ar":"فَلَاةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the n. un.,] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuliY~N","text_ar":"فُلِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) or this is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falFA","text_ar":"فَلًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) and [so are]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"filiY~N","text_ar":"فِلِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuluw~N","text_ar":"فُلُوٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is the original of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuliY~N","text_ar":"فُلِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"filiY~N","text_ar":"فِلِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (CK,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afolaA='N","text_ar":"اَفْلَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is [likewise] pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falFA","text_ar":"فَلًا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, M, Msb, K. *) ―         -b2-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axuw","text_ar":"اَخُو"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfalaApi","text_ar":"الفَلَاةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man of the desert:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one who travels in the desert"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deserts."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aibonu AlfalaApi","text_ar":"اِبْنُ الفَلَاةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HirobaA='","text_ar":"حِرْبَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"male chameleon"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (T in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bnY","text_ar":"بنى"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["M","K","Msb","T","S","TA","CK"]}]}}